-      "trad": "I hired Cloé for my wedding and I’m absolutely delighted with her work. She’s a professional who’s attentive and very gentle. After my trial, she really listened to my feedback and adapted perfectly to my expectations. The result: my wedding day look was exactly what I had envisioned. Thank you, Cloé, for your support during my bridal preparation and for taking such good care of my guests as well.",
